<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your PixiCred Account Has Been Closed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2c3e50;">Account Closure Confirmation</h1>
  <p>Dear Valued Customer,</p>
  <p>
    Your PixiCred credit card account (<strong>{{accountId}}</strong>) has been closed at your request.
    The closure took effect on {{closedAt}}.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you wish to open a new PixiCred account in the future, you are welcome to reapply at any time.
    Visit <a href="{{baseUrl}}/apply">{{baseUrl}}/apply</a> to submit a new application.
  </p>
  <p>
    Thank you for being a PixiCred customer. We hope to serve you again in the future.
  </p>
  <p>Sincerely,<br />The PixiCred Team</p>
</body>
</html>
